     A            EKSKMM         2  0       COLHDG('DLT MM')
     A            EKSKDD         2  0       COLHDG('DLT DD')
      *JW         (FOR VW -->PACKAGE TYPE, 11=RETURNABLE, 22=EXPENDABLE )
     A            EKKOYY         4  0       COLHDG('UPD YY')
     A            EKKOMM         2  0       COLHDG('UPD MM')
     A            EKKODD         2  0       COLHDG('UPD DD')
